headline: How Recent AI Moves And Lower Targets Are Rewriting The Story For GoDaddy (GDDY)
summary: What Changed in the GoDaddy Price Target The latest research tweaks on GoDaddy keep the fair value estimate essentially flat, with only a small adjustment from US$175.06 to US$175.00 per share, but the inputs behind that number tell you more than the headline itself. A slightly higher discount rate of 9.71% and a modestly higher revenue growth assumption of 6.99% reflect analysts trying to balance cautious macro views with interest in the company’s AI driven product pipeline.
